ergy pulling\n37:25- Scalp massage\n40:05- Cleaning your eyes\n45:08- Moisturizing your eyes\n47:47- Whispered outro\n__\n\nThanks for watching!!\nmuch love,\nJocie\n\nHi! My name is Jocie (they/she), and I'm just a human happy to be creating ASMR videos : )\n\nI post what I enjoy, meaning lots of:\n\nMAKEUP \u0026 SKINCARE\nPERSONAL ATTENTION\nFANTASY ROLEPLAYS\n\u0026 NATURE\n\nNew videos TUESDAYS 6PM EST and/or whenever else I can post!\n\nFor someone practicing to slow down \u0026 be kind to themselves, I find ASMR gives us a chance for pause, encouraging us to take time for self care and to prioritize our wellbeing. I hope we can all use this channel to practice love, laugh a little, and relax ♡ SUBSCRIBE and join in on the tingles!\n\n*Shopping from the tagged products helps me receive a small commission from your purchase. Know that there's no pressure whatsoever to buy anything. Thank you for the support : )\n#asmr","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":970,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ040EGAciEwia-frcsZ6UAxXVE1cBHWyhMIhIh8e_uPPfspbNAcoBBC1QLWQ=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXNiRzhPczMyOW1sR0NIN1hNX2d3VGduZ0d5d3xBQ3Jtc0tuREtac1loRVdGZDlHMVY0cng3RXpNa0UwZmlWNlExeWlfU0hvUklBSHcxd2JOajM2M1FqM1JycjJOd2RFUG0yVXBEMlBTc3AxeUZjMTZxQzZsOW9ZTjYwR3BTcHVRbVc3UkRPeEtpVTlPaC1MamJEQQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fffm.to%2Fjociebasmr\u0026v=zSzK_zcP44c","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXNiRzhPczMyOW1sR0NIN1hNX2d3VGduZ0d5d3xBQ3Jtc0tuREtac1loRVdGZDlHMVY0cng3RXpNa0UwZmlWNlExeWlfU0hvUklBSHcxd2JOajM2M1FqM1JycjJOd2RFUG0yVXBEMlBTc3AxeUZjMTZxQzZsOW9ZTjYwR3BTcHVRbVc3UkRPeEtpVTlPaC1MamJEQQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fffm.to%2Fjociebasmr\u0026v=zSzK_zcP44c","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":1018,"length":16,"onTap":{"