TOK\n  / jociebasmr  \n__\n\n✧ TIMESTAMPS ✧\n\n0:00- Whispered intro and giving you tea\n3:50- Getting you comfy\n8:30- Misting you with cologne\n12:00- Calming your vagus nerve\n18:20- Self massage\n21:40- Massaging your shoulders\n25:04- 5-4-3-2-1 Grounding\n27:52- Energy pulling\n37:25- Scalp massage\n40:05- Cleaning your eyes\n45:08- Moisturizing your eyes\n47:47- Whispered outro\n__\n\nThanks for watching!!\nmuch love,\nJocie\n\nHi! My name is Jocie (they/she), and I'm just a human happy to be creating ASMR videos : )\n\nI post what I enjoy, meaning lots of:\n\nMAKEUP \u0026 SKINCARE\nPERSONAL ATTENTION\nFANTASY ROLEPLAYS\n\u0026 NATURE\n\nNew videos TUESDAYS 6PM EST and/or whenever else I can post!\n\nFor someone practicing to slow down \u0026 be kind to themselves, I find ASMR gives us a chance for pause, encouraging us to take time for self care and to prioritize our wellbeing. I hope we can all use this channel to practice love, laugh a little, and relax ♡ SUBSCRIBE and join in on the tingles!\n\n*Shopping from the tagged products helps me receive a small commission from your purchase. Know that there's no pressure whatsoever to buy anything. Thank you for the support : )\n#asmr","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":970,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ040EGAciEwia-frcsZ6UAxXVE1cBHWyhMIhIh8e_uPPfspbNAcoBBC1QLWQ=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa0ZoU1BiSUcxTVFPVW45bURxNWE4VEpfNDFBQXxBQ3Jtc0tsYzN6UGl5cTZjNEViVFY2azQwYW5oTWNtUmtZV1E5bzQ4Mm1IeFp6YmJwUUF6dUxidmJfOXV5a09wMXllQkFUV1h4a1V5cWxCaE1JSFZJUVc4cjJvTVUwLU13MWI0eXJWU0UzYzVMV21VUHIyVW42cw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fffm.to%2Fjociebasmr\u0026v=zSzK_zcP44c","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa0ZoU1BiSUcxTVFPVW45bURxNWE4VEpfNDFBQXxBQ3Jtc0tsYzN6UGl5cTZjNEViVFY2azQwYW5oTWNt